{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-js","path":"/android-automation/","result":{"data":{"cur":{"id":"39c63dc4-3fde-54be-88d4-f9aeaed5a7e4","html":"<h1 id=\"0-들어가며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#0-%EB%93%A4%EC%96%B4%EA%B0%80%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"0 들어가며 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>0. 들어가며</h1>\n<p>임의의 애플리케이션에 내가 원하는 동작을 컴퓨터가 자동으로 시행하게 해보아야겠다고 생각했다. 그 중 가장 구현하기 쉬운 방식을 찾아보아, Android Studio + Appium + Python을 사용하는 방식을 택하였다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"1-준비사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EC%A4%80%EB%B9%84%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"1 준비사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 준비사항</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-1-android-studio\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-1-android-studio\" aria-label=\"1 1 android studio permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-1. Android Studio</h2>\n<p>최신 버전의 <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/studio\">Android Studio</a>를 설치한다.\n프로그램을 실행한 후, More Actions을 눌러 SDK Manager로 간다. Android 13.0 (Tiramisu)을 다운로드한다. 화면 상단에 보면 <code class=\"language-text\">Android SDK Location</code>이 있는데, 나중에 이 경로를 쓸 것이니 미리 복사해두기 바란다. 일반적으로 아래와 같을 것이다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Windows: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Users\\[사용자 이름]\\AppData\\Local\\Android\\SDK</code></li>\n<li>Mac: <code class=\"language-text\">/Users/[사용자 이름]/Library/Android/sdk</code>이다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.55555555555556%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-1.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-1.png\"\n        src=\"/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/37523/android-automation-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/e9ff0/android-automation-1.png 180w,\n/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/f21e7/android-automation-1.png 360w,\n/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/37523/android-automation-1.png 720w,\n/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/302a4/android-automation-1.png 1080w,\n/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/07a9c/android-automation-1.png 1440w,\n/static/e37b2060e5aef35541135b05b5f0802a/ade5e/android-automation-1.png 2188w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>다시 처음화면으로 돌아가 More Actions의 Virtual Device Manager로 간다. Create Device를 누르고 Pixel 4, Android 13.0 (Tiramisu)를 선택한다. 이후 플레이 버튼을 누르면 가상 안드로이드 디바이스가 실행된다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-2.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-2.png\"\n        src=\"/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/37523/android-automation-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/e9ff0/android-automation-2.png 180w,\n/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/f21e7/android-automation-2.png 360w,\n/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/37523/android-automation-2.png 720w,\n/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/302a4/android-automation-2.png 1080w,\n/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/07a9c/android-automation-2.png 1440w,\n/static/64dbe5033f6a33c361cca6fec1850024/7575b/android-automation-2.png 1608w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-2-java-se-8\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-2-java-se-8\" aria-label=\"1 2 java se 8 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-2. Java SE 8</h2>\n<p>기존에 Java 8을 쓰는 사람은 건너뛰면 된다. <a href=\"https://www.oracle.com/kr/java/technologies/javase/javase8u211-later-archive-downloads.html\">JDK, JRE 8 Oracle 페이지</a>에 들어가서 JDK(Java Development Kit)와 JRE(Java Runtime Environment)를 설치한다.\nOracle 회원가입 및 로그인을 해야 하므로, 귀찮은 사람들을 위해 아래에 Oracle 서버의 direct download 링크를 넣어두겠다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/GetFile/1.8.0_331-b09/165374ff4ea84ef0bbd821706e29b123/windows-i586/jdk-8u331-windows-x64.exe\">JDK 8 Windows</a>\n<a href=\"https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/GetFile/1.8.0_331-b09/165374ff4ea84ef0bbd821706e29b123/unix-i586/jdk-8u331-macosx-x64.dmg\">JDK 8 Mac</a>\n<a href=\"https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/AutoDL?BundleId=246264_165374ff4ea84ef0bbd821706e29b123\">JRE 8 Windows</a>\n<a href=\"https://javadl.oracle.com/webapps/download/AutoDL?BundleId=246255_165374ff4ea84ef0bbd821706e29b123\">JRE 8 Mac</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-3-appium-server-gui\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-3-appium-server-gui\" aria-label=\"1 3 appium server gui permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-3. Appium Server GUI</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/appium/appium-desktop/releases/tag/v1.22.3-4\">Appium Server GUI</a>를 설치한 뒤 실행한다. Host는 <code class=\"language-text\">127.0.0.1</code>로, Port는 <code class=\"language-text\">4723</code>로 설정한다. Edit Configurations를 누르면 환경 변수를 설정하는 창이 뜬다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-3.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-3.png\"\n        src=\"/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/37523/android-automation-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/e9ff0/android-automation-3.png 180w,\n/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/f21e7/android-automation-3.png 360w,\n/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/37523/android-automation-3.png 720w,\n/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/302a4/android-automation-3.png 1080w,\n/static/ce4be1d302f445a280c67332cdcda2c8/85e74/android-automation-3.png 1436w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<code class=\"language-text\">ANDROID_HOME</code>에는 앞에서 복사했던 <code class=\"language-text\">Android SDK Location</code>를 넣어준다. JAVA_HOME에는 설치한 JDK의 경로를 넣어준다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Windows: <code class=\"language-text\">C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jdk-[버전명]</code></li>\n<li>Mac: <code class=\"language-text\">/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/jdk[버전명].jdk</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Mac의 경우, Finder > Go > Go To Folder로 가서 <code class=\"language-text\">/Library/Java/JavaVirtualMachines/</code>을 입력하면 jdk 폴더가 나올 것이다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 115.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-4.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-4.png\"\n        src=\"/static/8756d7db81507a7733eeda464b5e51aa/37523/android-automation-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8756d7db81507a7733eeda464b5e51aa/e9ff0/android-automation-4.png 180w,\n/static/8756d7db81507a7733eeda464b5e51aa/f21e7/android-automation-4.png 360w,\n/static/8756d7db81507a7733eeda464b5e51aa/37523/android-automation-4.png 720w,\n/static/8756d7db81507a7733eeda464b5e51aa/7e4a6/android-automation-4.png 952w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n다 끝났으면 startServer를 누른다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-4-appium-inspector\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-4-appium-inspector\" aria-label=\"1 4 appium inspector permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-4. Appium Inspector</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/appium/appium-inspector/releases\">Appium Insepctor</a>를 설치한 뒤 실행한다. Remote Host가 <code class=\"language-text\">127.0.0.1</code>, Remote Port가 <code class=\"language-text\">4723</code>인지 확인한다. Remote Path는 <code class=\"language-text\">/wd/hub/</code>로 설정한다. Desired Capabilities에 [<code class=\"language-text\">platformName</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">text</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">Android</code>]를 추가한다. (추가하지 않을 시 작동이 안 된다.)\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-5.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-5.png\"\n        src=\"/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/37523/android-automation-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/e9ff0/android-automation-5.png 180w,\n/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/f21e7/android-automation-5.png 360w,\n/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/37523/android-automation-5.png 720w,\n/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/302a4/android-automation-5.png 1080w,\n/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/07a9c/android-automation-5.png 1440w,\n/static/e8bb11139e827be9b335a5079c42caf6/864a6/android-automation-5.png 2276w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n다 끝났으면 Start Session을 누른다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-5-python\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-5-python\" aria-label=\"1 5 python permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1-5. Python</h2>\n<p>기본적으로 Python 3와 IDE(PyCharm, VS Code 등)이 설치되어 있어야 한다. 또 모듈을 설치하기 위해 pip도 있어야 한다.\n<a href=\"https://www.python.org/downloads/\">Python 3</a>\n<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/download\">VS Code</a>\n<a href=\"https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installation/\">pip</a>\nTerminal 혹은 Command Prompt에 아래를 입력한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">pip install Appium-Python-Client</code> : Appium의 파이썬 클라이언트를 설치한다.</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">pip install selenium</code> : selenium의 여러 함수(By 등)을 사용하기 위해 설치한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"2-코드-작성-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C-%EC%9E%91%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"2 코드 작성 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 코드 작성 방법</h1>\n<p>Appium은 selenium의 웹 크롤링과 유사한 방식으로 작동된다. 가령, Google Calendar 앱 내에서 검색 버튼을 클릭하고 싶다고 해보자.\n우선 Android Studio에서 구동하고 있는 가상 안드로이드에서 Google Calendar에 들어간다. 이후 Appium Inspector의 새로고침 버튼(Refresh Source And Screenshot)을 누른다. 그러면 Appium Inspector에 현재 휴대폰 화면이 뜰 것이다. Select Elements 툴로 검색 버튼을 누르면, 그것에 해당하는 element를 아래 사진에서와 같이 보여준다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.11111111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"android-automation-6.png\"\n        title=\"android-automation-6.png\"\n        src=\"/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/37523/android-automation-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/e9ff0/android-automation-6.png 180w,\n/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/f21e7/android-automation-6.png 360w,\n/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/37523/android-automation-6.png 720w,\n/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/302a4/android-automation-6.png 1080w,\n/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/07a9c/android-automation-6.png 1440w,\n/static/ebf0becc32998c7281fe36b53d376abd/0a17b/android-automation-6.png 3720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\n이때 필요한 정보는 <code class=\"language-text\">id</code> 혹은 <code class=\"language-text\">xpath</code>이다. 이것을 이용하면 파이썬 코드를 작성하여 자동화할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">from appium import webdriver\nfrom selenium.webdriver.common.by import By\n\ndesired_capabilities = {\n    \"platformName\": \"Android\",\n    \"platformVersion\": \"13\",\n    \"deviceName\": \"Android Emulator\",\n}\n\ndriver = webdriver.Remote(\"http://127.0.0.1:4723/wd/hub\", desired_capabilities)\ndriver.find_element(By.ID, \"com.google.android.calendar:id/action_search\").click()</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-1-android-studio\">1-1. Android Studio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-2-java-se-8\">1-2. Java SE 8</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-3-appium-server-gui\">1-3. Appium Server GUI</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-4-appium-inspector\">1-4. Appium Inspector</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#1-5-python\">1-5. Python</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","excerpt":"0. 들어가며 임의의 애플리케이션에 내가 원하는 동작을 컴퓨터가 자동으로 시행하게 해보아야겠다고 생각했다. 그 중 가장 구현하기 쉬운 방식을 찾아보아, Android Studio + Appium + Python을 사용하는 방식을 택하였다. 1. 준비사항 1-1. Android Studio 최신 버전의 Android Studio를 설치한다.\n프로그램을 실행한 후, More Actions을 눌러 SDK Manager로 간다. Android 13.0 (Tiramisu)을 다운로드한다. 화면 상단에 보면 이 있는데, 나중에 이 경로를 쓸 것이니 미리 복사해두기 바란다. 일반적으로 아래와 같을 것이다. Windows:  Mac: 이다.  다시 처음화면으로 돌아가 More Actions의 Virtual Device Manager로 간다. Create Device를 누르고 Pixel 4, Android 13.0 (Tiramisu)를 선택한다. 이후 플레이 버튼을 누르면 가상 안드로이드 디바이스…","frontmatter":{"date":"January 17, 2023","title":"안드로이드 앱 자동화","categories":"자동화","author":"이승준","emoji":"😀"},"fields":{"slug":"/android-automation/"}},"next":{"id":"cf8b2fc9-3e7d-5764-8b48-9b7eec23101f","html":"<h1 id=\"text\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#text\" aria-label=\"text permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Text</h1>\n<h2 id=\"document-type-definition\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#document-type-definition\" aria-label=\"document type definition permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Document Type Definition</h2>\n<p>문서 형식을 정의하는 태그로, 출력할 웹 페이지의 형식을 브라우저에 전달한다.문서의 최상단에 위치해야 하며, HTML5는 아래를 사용한다.\n<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html></code></p>\n<h2 id=\"html\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#html\" aria-label=\"html permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>html</h2>\n<p>모든 HTML 요소의 부모 요소이다. (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!DOCTYPE></code> 제외)\n한국어를 사용할 때 <code class=\"language-text\">lang</code> attribute을 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML>\n&lt;html lang=\"ko\">\n  &lt;head>&lt;/head>\n  &lt;body>&lt;/body>\n&lt;/html></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"head\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#head\" aria-label=\"head permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>head</h2>\n<p>metadata를 포함하기 위한 태그.</p>\n<h3 id=\"title\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#title\" aria-label=\"title permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>title</h3>\n<p>문서의 제목을 정의하며, 이는 브라우저의 탭에 표시된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;title>문서 제목&lt;/title></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"style\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#style\" aria-label=\"style permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>style</h3>\n<p>HTML 문서의 스타일 정보를 정의한다. 주로 이 방식 대신 외부 CSS 파일을 불러온다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style>\n    body {\n        background-color: yellow;\n        color: blue;\n    }\n&lt;/style></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"link\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#link\" aria-label=\"link permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>link</h3>\n<p>외부 리소스와의 연계 정보를 정의한다. 외부 CSS 파일을 불러올 때 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\"></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"script\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#script\" aria-label=\"script permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>script</h3>\n<p>client-side JavaScript를 정의한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script>\n    document.addEventListener('click', function () {\n        alert('Clicked!');\n    });\n&lt;/script></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">src</code> attribute를 사용하여 외부 JavaScript 파일을 불러올 때도 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;script src=\"main.js\">&lt;/script></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"meta\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#meta\" aria-label=\"meta permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>meta</h3>\n<p>메타데이터의 정의에 사용된다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">charset</code> attribute:</li>\n<li>` 브라우저가 사용할 문자셋을 정의한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;meta charset=\"utf-8\"></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#document-type-definition\">Document Type Definition</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#html\">html</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#head\">head</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#title\">title</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#style\">style</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#link\">link</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#script\">script</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#meta\">meta</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 08, 2023","title":"HTML 태그 정리","categories":"HTML","author":"이승준","emoji":"😀"},"fields":{"slug":"/html-tag/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://leesj-dev.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":"leesj-dev/leesj-dev.github.io"}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/android-automation/","nextSlug":"/html-tag/","prevSlug":""}},"staticQueryHashes":["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}